title: VMMC Safdarjung Hospital Recruitment 2025 - Walk - in for 89 Junior Resident Posts
description: The Vardhman Mahavir Medical College and Safdarjung Hospital (VMMC Safdarjung Hospital) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 89 Junior Resident Posts. Interested and eligible candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the deadline. Candidates who have completed their MBBS, BDS can apply for the VMMC Safdarjung Recruitment 2025 . The interested applicants can attend the walk-in interview.
